{"tid":2212963,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"國軍訂88杯突然棄單　蔡英文親赴飲料店買爆150杯","createTime":"2020-09-22T07:48:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-22T11:34:36.000Z","uid":289214,"like":60,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"8f4b572d72883bb11d21893183f042ec160a2bd9","tid":2212963,"uid":289214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T07:48:10.000Z","msg":"澎湖海軍單位日前向在地飲料點訂了88杯手搖飲，但剛好碰到共軍再次擾台，緊急出勤守護家園，雖然手搖飲店當時已做了44杯被臨時棄單，但店家沒有怨言力挺國軍。總統蔡英文22日親赴澎湖視察，在空檔時間也特別前往該手搖飲店，親自埋單150杯飲料。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址: 快訊／國軍訂88杯突然棄單 蔡英文親赴飲料店買爆150杯 | ETtoday政治新聞 | ETtoday新聞雲 <a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20200922/1814791.htm#ixzz6YkrCfeSg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20200922%2F1814791.htm%23ixzz6YkrCfeSg&d=UI3sabJMorhQDzR%2BXF3zEeQdxvW7LhoH5lY2nOShEJQ%3D&h=51d80ca6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20200922/1814791.htm#ixzz6YkrCfeSg</a><br />\nFollow us: @ETtodaynet on Twitter | ETtoday on Facebook<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"blue\"><strong>買咁多杯做死人</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db41a72f49aa4b045115eaae962394709c5f4c4c","tid":2212963,"uid":117301,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T07:50:27.000Z","msg":"羨慕台灣 <br />\n有自己軍隊 又有貼地既總統<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1732036f8eff7c6fccdcb5c4ca8e23791f1af741","tid":2212963,"uid":60057,"like":21,"dislike":2,"score":19,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T07:53:40.000Z","msg":"件事ENGLISH處理得好好，間鋪頭話唔怨國軍但又POST上網係咩玩法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"372709ea45a0e67711aab0277d3903539b023532","tid":2212963,"uid":44454,"like":18,"dislike":3,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T07:54:28.000Z","msg":"維尼在空檔時間也特別前往該手搖飲店，親自埋葬了手搖店店長。"},{"pid":"158df56892683fc96178274932589f0ee81044e8","tid":2212963,"uid":6845,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"1732036f8eff7c6fccdcb5c4ca